Recently sold: $279,900. Yes our home IS for sale! Please dont hesitate to call we are in the middle of a fresh great room and kitchen remodel we just had quartz countertops and a new DEEP stainless steel farm sink installed. New pictures coming upon completion. 

Call 218-780-4625 to set up a showing

2.5% commision for realtors.  Home will be listed on the mls soon. Get in now to get a jump on the other buyers. 
Low low low taxes (up to $250/month less than a comparable home located in cloquet) and lower insurance and heating costs along with private well and septic means you can afford more home for your money. 

Private out of town location on dead end road. House is set towards the middle of 10 acre lot for that wonderful privacy youve been missing. No busy highway here yet the proximity to hwy 2 makes your morning commute a breeze! 25 minutes to hermantown 25 minutes to cloquet.  Located in the desirable south ridge school district your forever home awaits. The one level living means that you can grow to old age in Comfort. Both private and County plowing are available in the winter time as well as multiple options for garbage service. 1 gig or 1000mbps  High-speed internet is coming this fall or early next spring. This means you can live with the Quiet comfort of country living and still have all of the Intown amenities.
